         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Christmas-day / 1886. ¶  ¶ It is with much delight, hon. and venerable Sir, that I learn of the final arrangements made by you, for receiving the msc. of the Myoporinae in 1887. This will give me time...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">86.12.25</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Alphonse de Candolle</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Bibliothèque des Conservatoire et Jardin botaniques, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Christmas-day / 1886.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is with much delight, hon. and venerable Sir, that I learn of the final arrangements made by you, for receiving the msc. of the <name key="Myoporinae">Myoporinae</name> in 1887. This will give me time, to complete before the dichotomous Key to the system of Vict. plants.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B88.13.03.</p>
               </note> I have material, to include also the extra austr. spec., your M. Mauritianum &amp;c., but <name key="Spielmannia">Spielmannia</name> must be excluded.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For Mr Vesque I beg to include specimens of an Australian <name key="Kayea">Kayea</name> &amp;c, as a contribution to his monography of <name key="Guttiferae">Guttiferae</name>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>May the new year to you and all those dear to you, be one replete with happiness.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">A complete series of typical specimens of the <name key="Myoporinae">Myoporinae</name> will be sent to you with the msc.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's proposed work for Candolle on the <name key="Myoporinae">Myoporinae</name> was never published.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Guttiferae">Guttiferae</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
